Spritely Goblins
****************

This is the manual for Spritely Goblins
(https://spritely.institute/goblins/), a distributed object programming
environment.  Spritely Goblins is maintained by Spritely Networked
Communities Institute (https://spritely.institute/) and is built to be
the core layer for building broader decentralized networking
technologies.

   Both this manual and Guile Goblins itself are released under Apache
v2.  See *note License:: for more information.

